item.title: Automator (series) - By Devoid Of Joy (story, score, soundtrack)
item.dc:creator: Devoid-of-joy
item.description:
I’m an indifferent pacifist I do hate school but not as much as I hate guns. As for the art, it’s open for interpretations it’s just meaningless absurdity. As for the harsh vibes, I blame the heavy electronics I listen too, kind of numbs one to abrasive noises. Thanks for the listen

Oh, I thought about making a playlist or something along those lines but alas that thought came after I had already uploaded.
I’m not the smartest when it comes to this series of tubes that others surf easily and care free.
